eas_text: A civil authority has issued A REQUIRED MONTHLY TEST for the following counties or areas: Walla Walla; Benton; Franklin, WA; at 05:25 PM ON DEC 10, 2025 Effective until 06:25 PM. Message from WSLF/CAP.
extra_text: This is Walla Walla County Emergency Management conducting a required Monthly test of the Emergency Alert System. In the event of an emergency this system would bring you important information. The following tones will conclude this test This is a test, no action is required.
